scene.message:
White Girl: This is no time{nl}
to be doing this...{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey,{nl}
have you seen me?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ?{nl}
What's this kid saying?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey there, little miss,{nl}
why are you in a place{nl}
like this? It's dangerous,{nl}
go on home now.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Ayase!{nl}
There's no way a normal girl{nl}
would be in a place{nl}
like this!!{waitkey}{clearbox}She's not making any sense.{nl}
She might not even be human!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Ayase!{nl}
Can't you think things{nl}
through a little calmly?{waitkey}{clearbox}There's no way a girl{nl}
would be here!{waitkey}{nl}
She's a Monster!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Oh, shut up already!{nl}
Nitpicking every little thing{waitkey}{clearbox}I just called out because{nl}
she looked like she was in{nl}
trouble! I'm not cold-blooded{nl}
like you!!{waitkey}{ret}

White Girl: Mai-chan isn't{nl}
lost, and isn't{nl}
a demon either.{waitkey}{clearbox}More importantly,{nl}
have you seen me?{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm wearing the same{nl}
clothes as you big sisters{nl}
and a white mask.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: A student here?{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry, but I don't know{nl}
any students wearing{nl}
masks.{waitkey}{ret}

Mai: Huh!?{nl}
Where was she?{nl}
Tell me!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Uh, yeah.{nl}
On this floor.{nl}
But I forget exactly where.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Uh, yeah.{waitkey}{clearbox}I think it was a stage-like{nl}
spot on the 8th floor.{nl}
But she went{nl}
further up, it seems.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That girl...{nl}
I feel like I've seen her{nl}
somewhere.{waitkey}{nl}
But who was she...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What a cutie~{nl}
If I lock her down now,{nl}
in ten years...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: A girl in a place{nl}
like this{waitkey}{nl}
must be a Monster!{waitkey}{ret}
